title: Congressman Roger Marshall on USMCA

description:
Kevin spoke with Brendan Buck, Former Spokesman & Advisor to House Speaker Paul Ryan and Partner at Seven Letter and Al Mottur, Partner at Brownstein, Hyatt, Farber & Schreck. They discussed impeachment and 2020 elections.

Congressman Roger Marshall also called in to discuss USMCA.
